# Description: Showcase ace-llm alias query, provider listing, and fallback-oriented config flow
# Tags: ace-llm,docs,getting-started

Output ace-llm/docs/demo/ace-llm-getting-started.gif

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1100
Set Height 680

Type 'ace-llm gflash "Summarize why fallback matters in 2 bullets" --quiet'
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type 'ace-llm --list-providers'
Enter
Sleep 4s

Type 'ace-llm --list-aliases'
Enter
Sleep 3s
